\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><span class=\"wp-image-60110 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:1024px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:52.34375%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/0d1568f2b15891c138461d33cb338c3e/b95e4/GH-2020-Raffle-FB-Post-1200x630-1.jpg 256w,\n/static/0d1568f2b15891c138461d33cb338c3e/1779b/GH-2020-Raffle-FB-Post-1200x630-1.jpg 512w,\n/static/0d1568f2b15891c138461d33cb338c3e/87945/GH-2020-Raffle-FB-Post-1200x630-1.jpg 1024w,\n/static/0d1568f2b15891c138461d33cb338c3e/5a523/GH-2020-Raffle-FB-Post-1200x630-1.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcSet=\"/static/0d1568f2b15891c138461d33cb338c3e/b95e4/GH-2020-Raffle-FB-Post-1200x630-1.jpg 256w,\n/static/0d1568f2b15891c138461d33cb338c3e/1779b/GH-2020-Raffle-FB-Post-1200x630-1.jpg 512w,\n/static/0d1568f2b15891c138461d33cb338c3e/87945/GH-2020-Raffle-FB-Post-1200x630-1.jpg 1024w,\n/static/0d1568f2b15891c138461d33cb338c3e/5a523/GH-2020-Raffle-FB-Post-1200x630-1.jpg 1200w\" src=\"/static/0d1568f2b15891c138461d33cb338c3e/87945/GH-2020-Raffle-FB-Post-1200x630-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/0d1568f2b15891c138461d33cb338c3e/b95e4/GH-2020-Raffle-FB-Post-1200x630-1.jpg 256w,\n/static/0d1568f2b15891c138461d33cb338c3e/1779b/GH-2020-Raffle-FB-Post-1200x630-1.jpg 512w,\n/static/0d1568f2b15891c138461d33cb338c3e/87945/GH-2020-Raffle-FB-Post-1200x630-1.jpg 1024w,\n/static/0d1568f2b15891c138461d33cb338c3e/5a523/GH-2020-Raffle-FB-Post-1200x630-1.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"/static/0d1568f2b15891c138461d33cb338c3e/b95e4/GH-2020-Raffle-FB-Post-1200x630-1.jpg 256w,\n/static/0d1568f2b15891c138461d33cb338c3e/1779b/GH-2020-Raffle-FB-Post-1200x630-1.jpg 512w,\n/static/0d1568f2b15891c138461d33cb338c3e/87945/GH-2020-Raffle-FB-Post-1200x630-1.jpg 1024w,\n/static/0d1568f2b15891c138461d33cb338c3e/5a523/GH-2020-Raffle-FB-Post-1200x630-1.jpg 1200w\" src=\"/static/0d1568f2b15891c138461d33cb338c3e/87945/GH-2020-Raffle-FB-Post-1200x630-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:50px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Hear ye, hear ye, we do officially declare that the Kings and Queens of Good Hearts Gala is The PM Group’s favorite time of year. It’s a time we gather with clients, vendors, friends, and family to celebrate and raise money to support the work of crucial nonprofits in our community. It’s also an evening of entertainment, bidding, and casino games. Although this year’s event will look quite a bit different, the heart of it remains the same—continuing the mission of our agency to give back to deserving organizations in San Antonio.</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:50px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p>With the challenges this year has presented, our gala has transformed into the online Good Hearts Auction &amp; Raffle. We know that nonprofits need our help now more than ever! That’s why we are excited to be able to provide a way for our usual guests, and even those who may have never attended our gala, to be able to bid on items and take part in our raffle. September 14th through the 30th, head over to <a href=\"http://www.goodheartsraffle.org\"><strong>GOODHEARTSRAFFLE.ORG</strong></a> to get involved. All proceeds benefit the following nonprofits:</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><span class=\"wp-image-60111 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:1024px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:19.140625%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/695616e5b160b29a8682c1cec5f47b66/b95e4/GH-Nonprofits-Post-1200x630-1.jpg 256w,\n/static/695616e5b160b29a8682c1cec5f47b66/1779b/GH-Nonprofits-Post-1200x630-1.jpg 512w,\n/static/695616e5b160b29a8682c1cec5f47b66/87945/GH-Nonprofits-Post-1200x630-1.jpg 1024w,\n/static/695616e5b160b29a8682c1cec5f47b66/5a523/GH-Nonprofits-Post-1200x630-1.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcSet=\"/static/695616e5b160b29a8682c1cec5f47b66/b95e4/GH-Nonprofits-Post-1200x630-1.jpg 256w,\n/static/695616e5b160b29a8682c1cec5f47b66/1779b/GH-Nonprofits-Post-1200x630-1.jpg 512w,\n/static/695616e5b160b29a8682c1cec5f47b66/87945/GH-Nonprofits-Post-1200x630-1.jpg 1024w,\n/static/695616e5b160b29a8682c1cec5f47b66/5a523/GH-Nonprofits-Post-1200x630-1.jpg 1200w\" src=\"/static/695616e5b160b29a8682c1cec5f47b66/87945/GH-Nonprofits-Post-1200x630-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/695616e5b160b29a8682c1cec5f47b66/b95e4/GH-Nonprofits-Post-1200x630-1.jpg 256w,\n/static/695616e5b160b29a8682c1cec5f47b66/1779b/GH-Nonprofits-Post-1200x630-1.jpg 512w,\n/static/695616e5b160b29a8682c1cec5f47b66/87945/GH-Nonprofits-Post-1200x630-1.jpg 1024w,\n/static/695616e5b160b29a8682c1cec5f47b66/5a523/GH-Nonprofits-Post-1200x630-1.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"/static/695616e5b160b29a8682c1cec5f47b66/b95e4/GH-Nonprofits-Post-1200x630-1.jpg 256w,\n/static/695616e5b160b29a8682c1cec5f47b66/1779b/GH-Nonprofits-Post-1200x630-1.jpg 512w,\n/static/695616e5b160b29a8682c1cec5f47b66/87945/GH-Nonprofits-Post-1200x630-1.jpg 1024w,\n/static/695616e5b160b29a8682c1cec5f47b66/5a523/GH-Nonprofits-Post-1200x630-1.jpg 1200w\" src=\"/static/695616e5b160b29a8682c1cec5f47b66/87945/GH-Nonprofits-Post-1200x630-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>This year’s online auction has over 400 items thanks to the generous, continued support from our vendors and community partners. In addition to our auction, you may also purchase raffle tickets online for a&nbsp; chance to win your choice of a Mercedes C300 Sedan or GLA 250 SUV. The drawing will be held on October 5, 2020, so be sure to keep an eye on our Facebook page to stay up to date on our Good Hearts Auction &amp; Raffle news.</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:50px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Let it be known, Fair Ladies and Noble Knights are invited to feasting and festivities at our next Kings &amp; Queens of Good Hearts Gala on the twelfth and thirteenth of February, the year twenty twenty-one.</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://thepmgrp.com/\"><strong>About The PM Group</strong></a>: The PM Group was founded in 1988. For over 32 years, the agency has continued to grow and is San Antonio’s largest advertising agency. The PM Group’s client roster spans numerous industries including automotive, CPG, entertainment and sports marketing, legal, business services, non-profit, real estate and fitness. In addition, the agency hosts an annual Charity Gala that to date has raised millions of dollars for local San Antonio area non-profit organizations in the last 15 years! In the past 10 years, The PM Group has raised both directly and indirectly over $12 million for these charities. It is our way of giving back to the community that we so humbly serve.</p>\n","title":"The PM Group Transforms Annual Auction to Continue Supporting Local Nonprofits","seo":{"breadcrumbs":[{"text":"The PM Group Transforms Annual Auction to Continue Supporting Local Nonprofits","url":"/the-pm-group-transforms-annual-auction-to-continue-supporting-local-nonprofits/"}],"title":"The PM Group 2020 Charity Auction Supporting Local Nonprofits","metaDesc":"This year’s online auction has over 400 items thanks to the generous, continued support from our vendors and community partners...","focuskw":"Good Hearts","metaKeywords":"","metaRobotsNoindex":"index","metaRobotsNofollow":"follow","opengraphTitle":"The PM Group 2020 Charity Auction Supporting Local Nonprofits","opengraphDescription":"This year’s online auction has over 400 items thanks to the generous, continued support from our vendors and community partners...","opengraphImage":{"altText":"The PM Group - Good Hearts Auction and Raffle","sourceUrl":"https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/GH-2020-Raffle-FB-Post-2.jpg","srcSet":"https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/GH-2020-Raffle-FB-Post-2-300x300.jpg 300w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/GH-2020-Raffle-FB-Post-2-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/GH-2020-Raffle-FB-Post-2-150x150.jpg 150w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/GH-2020-Raffle-FB-Post-2-768x768.jpg 768w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-co